Package: intradayModel
Title: Modeling and Forecasting Financial Intraday Signals
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2023-05-17
Description: Package `intradayModel` uses state-of-the-art state-space models to facilitate
    the modeling, analyzing and forecasting of financial intraday signals. This package currently offers a
    univariate model for intraday trading volume, with new features on intraday volatility and
    multivariate models in development. It is a valuable tool for anyone interested in exploring
    intraday, algorithmic, and high-frequency trading.
